<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<!-- üé¨ ANIMACIONES CON GSAP                                     -->
<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê -->
<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        console.log("üìã Iniciando itinerario...");

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ESTADO INICIAL ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        gsap.set("#titulo-itinerario", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
        gsap.set("#evento-1, #evento-2, #evento-3, #evento-4, #evento-5", { opacity: 0, x: -30 });

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ANIMACI√ìN EN CASCADA ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        ScrollTrigger.create({
            trigger: "#contenedor-itinerario",
            start: "top 80%",
            onEnter: () => {
                const tl = gsap.timeline();

                tl.to("#titulo-itinerario", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    y: 0,
                    duration: 0.6,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                })
                .to("#evento-1", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 0.5,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                }, "-=0.2")
                .to("#evento-2", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 0.5,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-3", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 0.5,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-4", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 0.5,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-5", {
                    opacity: 1,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 0.5,
                    ease: "power2.out",
                }, "-=0.3");
            },
            onLeaveBack: () => {
                gsap.set("#titulo-itinerario", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
                gsap.set("#evento-1, #evento-2, #evento-3, #evento-4, #evento-5", { opacity: 0, x: -30 });
            },
        });

        // ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê ACTIVAR SI YA EST√Å VISIBLE ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
        ScrollTrigger.refresh();
        const triggerElement = document.querySelector("#contenedor-itinerario");
        if (triggerElement) {
            const rect = triggerElement.getBoundingClientRect();
            const isInView = rect.top < window.innerHeight * 0.8;
            
            if (isInView) {
                const tl = gsap.timeline();
                tl.to("#titulo-itinerario", { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.6 })
                .to("#evento-1", { opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.2")
                .to("#evento-2", { opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-3", { opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-4", { opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.3")
                .to("#evento-5", { opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.5 }, "-=0.3");
            }
        }

        console.log("üìã‚ú® Itinerario activado!");
    });
</script>